reviewText: I love all her yoga DVDs.  Strongly recommend any of her DVDs.
Amazing aid as a step to higher consciousness!
Can't explain it...just didn't flow, didn't feel right. The mantra session was ok!
She is amazing. I don't like yoga and she makes it simple and fun and deep. I love the music and her in general.

~~ THIS BOX SET OF MAYA FIENNES IS QUITE INVIGORATING  !!...THE BEST INVESTMENT I HAVE MADE FOR MYSELF & LOOK FORWARD TO MORE KUNDALINI YOGA... HAS MADE A BIG HAPPY CHANGE IN MY LIFE...FOR YOGA IS REAL LIFE ~~
